OL,3,CSheku Bayoh Inquiry to consider
OL,4,Capplication for recusal of chairman
OL,6,FThe Sheku Bayoh Inquiry is set to
OL,7,Fconsider issues around fairness from
OL,8,Fthe chairman, in a procedural hearing,
OL,9,Fafter it emerged he met the grieving
OL,10,Ffamily several times.
OL,12,FSheku Bayoh, 31, a father-of-two, died
OL,13,Fafter he was restrained by around six
OL,14,Fpolice officers who were called to
OL,15,FHayfield Road in Kirkcaldy, Fife, on
OL,16,FMay 3, 2015.
