OL,3,CSheku Bayoh Inquiry to consider
OL,4,Capplication for recusal of chairman
OL,6,FThe Crown Office decided not to take
OL,7,Flegal action against the police
OL,8,Finvolved following an investigation,
OL,9,Fbut the circumstances are being
OL,10,Fexamined at the inquiry.
OL,12,FThe procedural hearing on Thursday and
OL,13,FFriday was ordered by chairman Lord
OL,14,FBracadale to consider an application
OL,15,Ffor his own recusal. It will take
OL,16,Fplace at Capital House in Edinburgh.
OL,18,FIt comes after Lord Bracadale revealed
OL,19,Fhe has met with the family of Mr Bayoh
OL,20,Fon at least five occasions since the
OL,21,Finquiry began.
