OL,3,CSheku Bayoh Inquiry to consider
OL,4,Capplication for recusal of chairman
OL,6,FThe family's lawyer, Aamer Anwar,
OL,7,Fsuggested the procedural hearing alone
OL,8,Fcould "cost the public purse in excess
OL,9,Fof #1 million".
OL,11,FThe hearing follows an application for
OL,12,Frecusal of the chairman and an
OL,13,Fassessor on behalf of the Scottish
OL,14,FPolice Federation, Pc Craig Walker and
OL,15,FNicole Short.
OL,17,FRecusal is the legal process by which
OL,18,Fa judge or other adjudicator steps
OL,19,Faside from participating in a case due
OL,20,Fto potential bias, conflict of
OL,21,Finterest, or lack of impartiality.
