OL,3,CSheku Bayoh Inquiry to consider
OL,4,Capplication for recusal of chairman
OL,6,FMr Anwar said on behalf of the family:
OL,7,F"The procedural hearing follows an
OL,8,Fapplication for recusal of the chair
OL,9,Fand an assessor on behalf of the
OL,10,FScottish Police Federation, Pc Craig
OL,11,FWalker and Nicole Short.
OL,13,F"The hearing will focus on the
OL,14,Ffairness of the conduct and procedure
OL,15,Fadopted by the chair in meeting the
OL,16,Ffamilies of Sheku Bayoh.
OL,18,F"For the record, it is Lord Bracadale
OL,19,Fwho has ordered this hearing. The
OL,20,Finquiry will hear oral submissions
OL,21,Ffrom core participants.
