OL,3,CSheku Bayoh Inquiry to consider
OL,4,Capplication for recusal of chairman
OL,6,F"The family have watched so many
OL,7,Fparties who have literally sat on
OL,8,Ftheir hands for over 122 days of
OL,9,Fevidence, never publicly asking a
OL,10,Fquestion at a huge legal cost of #20
OL,11,Fmillion to the public, yet this
OL,12,Fhearing in terms of police lawyers
OL,13,Fcould cost the public in excess of #1
OL,14,Fmillion."
OL,16,FHe said the family are "not giving up"
OL,17,Fand that 10 years on from Mr Bayoh's
OL,18,Fdeath they will "once more call-out
OL,19,Fthe dangerous arrogance of a criminal
OL,20,Fjustice system that does not like
OL,21,Faccountability".
